title: Timeless/Classique python crossbody bag
description:
Chanel Python Mini Classic Flap bag, made of precious python leather, featuring silver tone hardware and a removable chain shoulder strap in milky colored leather. 
 
     The hologram sticker is attached to the inside, the serial number indicates that this bag was made in Italy between 2000 and 2002. 
 [[2 ]] Bag size: approx 16cm * 10cm * 5cm 
 Chain strap length: approx 105cm 
 
 There are slight signs of use throughout the bag (see photos), generally in very good vintage condition. 
 
 This bag comes with authenticity card, hologram sticker, original dust bag. 
 
 —————————————————————————————— 
 
 This beautiful bag is very practical, there are several ways to wear it (see photos) 
 
 1. Shoulder bag - wear as is 
 2. Fanny pack / fanny pack - remove the chain strap, place it in the "tunnel" at the back of this bag and attach the chain strap to your waist / buttocks. 
 3. Clutch - remove the chain strap and just use it as a pocket. 
 4. Handbag / shoulder bag - replace the original chain strap with a shorter strap. Please refer to the pearl bracelet in my photos (this pearl bracelet does not come with the bag)
Packaging: Dustbag, Card or certificate

title: Timeless/Classique leather handbag
description:
CHANEL BEIGE CAVIAR MEDIUM 2.55 CLASSIC DOUBLE FLAP BAG 
 
 Coco Chanel wanted to create a bag that was both classic and easy to carry, and this is how the Chanel flap bag was born. Originally inspired by military school bags of the 1920s, the unique handles allowed women to experience hands-free leisure. A true classic, the Chanel Flap bag is a bag that every woman should own. This beauty is made of caviar leather and comes with gold hardware. 
 
 This bag is on many waiting lists around the world and its price continues to increase. 
 
 The caviar version is highly coveted for its scratch-resistant versatility. This bag is medium beige in color. 
 
 Dimensions: 10 "W x 6" H x 2.5 "D 
 
 Condition: Excellent pre-loved condition - this bag has been used and maintained . 
 
 There are signs of wear or discoloration / discoloration. Includes dust bag and original Chanel box. 
 

Packaging: Dustbag, Original box

title: Timeless/Classique leather handbag
description:
Iconic CHANEL Vintage Jumbo Classic Flap Bag 24k GOLD Alloy GHW with oversized CCs
Year ca. 1997
A stunning bag that is hard to find and no longer available in boutiques, this CHANEL timeless quilted classic jumbo flap with oversized CC's now can be yours. ❤️
Iconic and ultra rare vintage Jumbo with XL CCs are treasured by celebrities and sometimes called “Beckham CHANEL bag” or “Nicole Richie bag”. The 24K gold-alloy CC and hardware make a great contrast to the deep black & shining leather.
CHANEL does not use gold in bag production since 2007, therefore vintage bags are extremely precious and gorgeous. ✨
- Golden hardware is extremely gold, especially in the evening lights, 
- Black leather with diamond quilting,
- Interior lined in burgundy lambskin,
- Signature oversized CC front clasp in 24k gold alloy plated hardware, as with the large chunky CHANEL chain,
- Classic back pocket, and interior has a side pocket and a side zipper pocket,
- Sticker inside with date code in perfect condition.
- Comes with ID Card. 
30 cm x 22 cm x 9 cm
This item is in very good condition with signs of use. Exterior is clean, with minimal scratches, one light pressed place (laid on its chain) on the back pocket of the bag, visible under inspection. Corners have light signs of rubbing. Gold hardware has minimal discoloration on the edges (max 5-10%), still deep yellow and very shiny, interwoven leather shows some rubbing. GOLD alloy plated turnlock has some little imperfections/ minor scratches, visible under close inspection. Leather interior has some thin scratches and some mini imperfections due to the age, visible under inspection. Very clean and tidy pockets, no flaws. 
Please see photos for details.

A Statement Bag and Collector’s Item.  💫

A very special CHANEL Celebrity or IT Piece, a  luxury masterpiece for your collection. ❤️ 
Please check my other collectible CHANEL items. 🌹

note: inside zipper is in working order but has lost clasp.

collectors! increasing in value annually!

title: Timeless/Classique leather handbag
description:
CHANEL Agneau Matelassé Jumbo Double Flap So Black All Black Gunmetal Hardware. 100% authentique. Livré avec boite d'origine, dustbag, livret d'entretien, pas de carte d'authenticité et est également livré avec chiffon de polissage. Vraiment joli sac obtenu en 2014. A été vu porté par Kim Kardashian. Ils ont fait ressortir la combinaison si noire à quelques reprises, d'abord la peau d'agneau que celle-ci est, puis le cuir de veau froissé et le chevron. La peau d'agneau pour moi est la plus belle. Recherché. Non disponible dans les boutiques Chanel. Il a été légèrement utilisé. Très bonne condition. La quincaillerie en bronze à la serrure cc est légèrement fanée s'il vous plaît voir les photos, l'intérieur très propre avec quelques rayures de surface. Les bords du sac sont à nouveau légèrement frottés, veuillez vous référer aux photos. Le matériel matelassé est toujours très gonflé et intacte. Quelques légères rayures superficielles très mineures et visibles, veuillez vous référer à toutes les images et peuvent en fournir plus si vous en avez besoin. De belles photos de sacs ne lui rendent pas justice. Éviscéré pour vendre mais besoin d'argent. Ce sac à bandoulière élégant est confectionné en cuir d'agneau luxueux matelassé en diamant noir. Le sac comprend des bretelles mates à maillons en bronze à mailles filetées de cuir noir et un verrou tournant Classic CC en bronze à canon mat. Cela ouvre le rabat avant sur un intérieur en cuir noir avec des poches plaquées. C'est un magnifique sac à bandoulière, idéal pour toutes les occasions, de Chanel!

title: Timeless/Classique linen bag
description:
Iconic CHANEL Vintage Linen Canvas Jumbo Classic Flap Bag 24k Gold Alloy GHW avec CC surdimensionnés 
 Année ca. 1995 
 Un sac étonnant qui est difficile à trouver et qui n'est plus disponible dans les boutiques, ce rabat géant classique matelassé intemporel CHANEL avec des CC surdimensionnés peut maintenant être le vôtre. ❤️ 
 
 Les Jumbo vintage iconiques et ultra rares avec des CC XL sont appréciés des célébrités et parfois appelés «sac Beckham Chanel» ou «sac Nicole Richie». La fermeture CC or surdimensionnée est un grand contraste avec la toile de lin beige profond. 
 La couleur est une toile de lin beige-taupe, sans effort chic et magnifique contrastant avec le matériel plaqué or jaune foncé 24 carats. [[2] ]] Les photos détaillées sont prises au soleil, certaines autres - sans. Sur les photos ensoleillées, la toile semble pâle / plus claire dans sa couleur. La vraie couleur est sur les gros plans et sur les images sans soleil. Le matériel doré est extrêmement brillant, surtout dans les lumières du soir! ✨ 
 - Toile CHANEL en beige profond avec matelassage en diamant, 
 - Intérieur doublé en cuir d'agneau beige, 
 - Fermoir avant CC surdimensionné signature en matériel plaqué or 24 carats, comme pour le grand chaîne CHANEL épaisse, 
 - Poche arrière classique, et l'intérieur a une poche latérale et une poche latérale zippée, 
 - Autocollant à l'intérieur avec code de date. 
 30 cm x 22 cm x 9 cm 
 Cet article est en très bon état avec quelques traces d'utilisation. Les coins sont propres avec un minimum de signes de frottement. Le matériel en or est jaune foncé et très brillant. La chaîne plaquée or est comme neuve, propre et brillante, la serrure en alliage d'or plaqué or présente quelques petites imperfections / rayures mineures au milieu, visibles sous une inspection minutieuse. L'extérieur est propre, mais l'intérieur en cuir présente quelques petites taches, visibles à l'inspection. Veuillez voir les photos pour plus de détails. 
 
 L'entretien de la toile est assez simple, en raison de sa structure. Si vous obtenez quelque chose dessus, utilisez un chiffon légèrement humide (ou juste un peu de savon sur un chiffon humide). 
 
 Un sac de déclaration et un objet de collection. 💫 
 
 Une célébrité CHANEL ou une pièce informatique très spéciale, un chef-d'œuvre pour votre collection. ❤️

title: Timeless/Classique tweed handbag
description:
Superb Chanel Classic Timeless Tweed Medium double flap bag with silver hardware. Made in France. Comes with authenticity card (96Х ХХХХ). Details: The approximate measurements are 25cm - 15cm - 6.5cm; the drop of the chain strap is 42 when it is single and 24 when it is double. The color is very pretty, soft pink - it's a pity that the photographs do not convey the true color, in real life it is much softer. Condition: Overall the bag is in excellent condition especially as it is a vintage tweed bag. It has been used very few times so it has spent most of its life stored in the box. The outer tweed is in great condition, it \ 's clean and has no marks and etc., the corners are perfect (please see the pictures). Under the flap and inside the interior pocket, the leather has scratches, scuffs (see photos), an almost invisible color that darkens in some parts - this happens over time (see photos) ; some dents, zipper scratches (please see pictures). The interior is clean and tidy, without any traces; the hologram present (it reads 96Х ХХХХ). Note: some slight traces of glue can be found in some of the edges, zip puller (we know this happens with luxury vintage bags over time); as they are tiny and can be found under closest inspection, mainly under the flap (please see pictures), they are not visible when wearing the bag. Silver hardware is shiny and crisp, I see no flaws, only slight (!) Insignificant darkening in parts of the leather part of the chain strap under very close inspection only. The imperfections mentioned do not affect the overall appearance of the bag at all, so I rate the condition "very good", especially for the vintage light colored tweed bags; it is clean, tidy and beautiful as can be seen from the detailed photos. This bag is timeless, so it will always be in fashion, it is one of the iconic Chanel bags whose price increases over the years. The purchase includes an authenticity card, a Chanel dust bag, a Chanel box, a small camellia folder, a small black care booklet (please see the photos).
Packaging: Dustbag, Original box, Card or certificate

100% Authentic Chanel Burgundy Caviar Leather Flap Shoulder Bag

 Crafted from fine burgundy diamond-quilted caviar leather and silver tone hardware, this bag is extremely versatile and can easily be coordinated with any outfit for any occasion. 
 Features a silver chain link strap threaded with burgundy leather, a quilted slit pocket on the outside back, a front flap that attaches with an iconic CC Mademoiselle twist lock in Chanel silver color that s opens onto an interior lined with burgundy leather with a wall pocket.

description:
This, ladies and gentlemen is a true classic.

Hermes Kelly in Togo leather and Camel colour. In original box, original dustbag, with original rain cover and an original separate pouch for a never used shoulder strap. This handbag was only used a few times and was always carefully stored. Two sides of the outside box have felt writing stating “Kelly Beige”.

The handbag shows the following signs of wear: minor scratches on metal elements that i’ve done my best to photograph so that they are visible to you, a small smudge on the backside of the left handle (as per pictures), a small scratch on one side of the bag (as per picture) and minor signs of wear on the corners of the bag (almost invisible without using zoom). There is also a minor detail on the inside of the bag on both trims where the straps (sangles) pass that may be a slight scratch though i’m not sure (still i took pictures of it).

The interior of the handbag is impeccable. The leather at the bottom, front and back of the bag is impeccable: No scratches on front, back or bottom.

Sold in original packaging as per pictures.

title: Kelly 32 leather handbag
description:
Rare combination of Epsom leather and the sought after Hermès 'grape' color for this Hermès Sellier 32 bag. Unlike most other leathers, the grain is pressed into the Epsom leather, giving it a laminated appearance. This type of compressed leather makes it very light but resistant, it is scratch resistant and water resistant. Leather is quite stiff, which means it keeps its shape without sagging. The color "Grape" is a rich, deep color that is a shade darker than purple. 
 
 the bag has been little used and is in very good condition - inside and out. There is a scuff on the bottom of one of the corners and a small scratch on the back which is barely noticeable - there is very little wear - please see the detail in the photos. Palladium hardware still has the protective plastic adhesive on the center of the hardware under the / Made in France logo. The bell with lock and keys has never been used (the plastic adhesive is still on the lock). 
 
 There is a large zippered pocket and two additional compartments inside the bag. 
 
 The bag is delivered with its shoulder strap, its bell with lock and keys (and its small bag) and a dust bag for the handbag.

description:
Magnificent Hermès Kelly Bag 32 Porosus crocodile skin in shiny chocolate brown color with golden hardware from 1962. This bag is made from the finest exotic skin that Hermès uses, and comes in a classic combination of brown and Golden. This item features the iconic clasp with two tabs and a one-piece straight flap. The bag has a top handle and includes a bell, pull tab, covered lock, keys and dust bag. The goatskin lining has three pockets: two open and one with zipper. The bag and the crocodile skin are in very good condition showing only a very small wear in the corners, almost imperceptible. The interior is in very good condition with no odor. A collector's item in excellent condition for the time. The blind stamp is "R". Just a comment: it belonged to the private collection of an opera legend although no evidence or information is provided on this.

It is safe to say that this is a collector's item as Hermès no longer uses Ardennes leather in its designs!

description: A superb vintage Kelly 28 by HERMÈS from the 60s, the most desired size, crafted in black Porosus crocodile leather, carefully hand-sewn to perfection and gold trim, has a trapezoidal structure, slightly wider at the base and a closure at right flap fixed by a golden metal bracelet. It has a short top handle. The interior is lined with black goat and has a zipped pocket with a lightning zipper and two open pockets on the opposite side. The stitching is remarkable, the leather in good condition and the closure works perfectly. Despite some small scratches on the material more imperceptible than the effects of the photos, and some traces of use, it is a bag in very very good condition for the time and which was cleaned a few years ago at the SPA Hermès ( no type of restoration) then returned to the closet until now. Signature: "Hermès Paris. Hidden stamp (before 1970)." Included: dustbag and Hermès Spa invoice. Does not include: bell, lock, keys and strap. It has always been very well maintained. A vintage Kelly 28 for Hermès collectors.

title: Kelly 28 leather handbag
description:
PLEASE READ THIS BEFORE MESSAGING. WARNING! THIS IS THE BAG YOU ARE WAITING FOR! And it is also the bag which further proves that a Hermès bag is a better investment than gold! This bag belongs to a family member who originally purchased it on a trip to Japan in 1998. The bag has been lovingly cared for for over twenty-two years! The bag is in exceptional condition. LEATHER: There are ZERO SCRATCHES on the surface of the leather. The only places you might see a tiny sign of use are near the glass on the back of the bag. I have attached a close up image of it here AND if you can't see it, it means it's too insignificant to notice. MATERIAL: The material is where you will be able to see all of the beautiful memories this bag has witnessed. I have attached some very detailed images for your review. All four legs are in exceptional condition. INTERIOR: This bag has always been worn with a bag insert since day one, so the interior is in near perfect condition. I will be including a brand new bag insert as part of the sale so you can continue to care for this bag for many years to come! The overall condition of this bag is a solid 9/10! PLEASE NOTE: Because this bag was purchased in 1998, there are some differences between this particular bag and the newer ones of the same model from Hermes 1) This bag does not have the D-rings that the newer models do here where you attach the strap to 2) The lining of the inside pockets is fabric instead of leather. Only bags produced after 2005 have a leather pocket I believe. 3) Dust bags are different colors and materials. WHY YOU SHOULD BUY THIS BAG: This particular bag truly embodies the timeless spirit of Hermès that transcends the test of time. This bag really had a great history in our family and witnessed all the beautiful times, but it is still kept in a conditional that you absolutely won't find in any other bag from the same period. This bag has meanings that go beyond a mere materialist. Whoever ends up buying this bag, I hope you can continue to take good care of her and maybe one day pass it on to someone you love.
Packaging: Dustbag

title: Kelly 32 leather handbag
description:
Pretty vintage Hermès Kelly bag in brown leather, size 32 with gold metal hardware. You can see the seal with the G in a circle belonging to the year 1977. The interior has a zipped pocket and on the closure of it, which is totally parallel to the zip, you can read Eclair. Also has two open pockets. The interior is in good condition. 
 The bag includes the padlock, the bell and the keys. Box and dust cover not included. 
 
 NOTE: 
 One end of the handles is almost completely loose and needs to be repaired. It has the Hermès Paris Made in France seal but the previous owner wanted to dye it himself and this made the seal almost hidden although under the asphalt you can see the full seal exists and this change made that in various parts from the bag it was you can see with the light like stained lines as if it were varnish. It has wear marks on the leather and in the corners, although the skin is very nice or very pleasant to the touch. I took the bag to Hermès and they told me it should be taken to the SPA for a restoration. The bag was originally purchased from an official store in Paris.

title: Kelly 35 leather handbag
description:
🍭 Un Bleu Céleste frais pour cette EDITION LIMITÉE Candy Kelly 35, en cuir epsom, avec intérieur et clochette Bleu Mykonos contrastés. 
 
 Un maître mondialement reconnu dans la production des nuances de bleu les plus étonnantes, Hermès donne nous voici un bleu clair moyen cool qui fonctionne aussi bien avec votre robe blanche d'été fluide qu'avec votre manteau d'ours en peluche confortable préféré 😍😍😍 
 Ce qui en fait un favori toute l'année parmi les fashionistas et les stars d'Hollywood 💙 
 
 Le sac est dans un état presque parfait, avec quelques plastiques encore sur le matériel. 
 très très faibles et minuscules rayures sur certains objets métalliques (trop petit pour bien photographier, mais J'ai essayé), pas de rayures ni de taches. Le moindre petit coin frottant (voir photo), pratiquement négligeable. 
 
 Epsom est en effet l'un des cuirs H les plus résistants aux rayures, parfaitement utilisable même par temps pluvieux aussi! 
 [[ 2]] Timbre dateur O en carré (2011), année de production de la plupart des modèles Candy. 
 
 Livré avec dustbag, mini dustbag pour accessoires, clochette, cadenas et clés, livret, housse de pluie 
 
 Veuillez jeter un œil à mes nombreux autres sacs H et plus 🙏

title: Kelly 28 leather handbag
description:
Hermès Kelly 28 - 1970 (A letter without form indicates that the bag was made between 1945 (A) and 1970 (Z)). 
 
 The Hermès "Kelly" bag gained its name and popularity during the 1950s, when Princess Grace Kelly was photographed using a Kelly to hide her early pregnancy. In fact, such a handcrafted gem that takes more than a day's work to be created from scratch can only be an accessory for princesses - by name and by nature. Extremely polished and chic, the Kelly bag is an exquisite piece of heavenly grace. A vintage Kelly bag also has that aura of charm and historical value that makes it unique and unmatched. 
 
 The Kelly is the most sought after bag and considered a fantastic investment for resale or for permanent use. It \ 's every woman \' s dream come true! The new Kelly bags can only be ordered and awaited by VIP HERMES members. at 40K more, impossible to obtain otherwise! The Kelly is classic, neutral and very very elegant. This vintage bag is in good used condition. There are signs of wear everywhere, some scuffs, slight aging of the leather, some small scratches, wear on the strap. This is a vintage bag, it is not in $ 45,000 condition. 
 
 Please view all photos and ask questions before purchasing. 
 
 Packaging: dust bag included

title: Birkin 40 leather handbag
description: Alongside its infamous sister bag, the Kelly, Hermès presents its iconic Birkin bag - the most recognized and requested bag in the world. Originally created in 1983 when Jean-Louis Dumas met Jane Birkin on a Paris-London flight. During the flight, she explained that she wanted a bag roomy enough for everything she needed and more, with plenty of pockets. Soon after, Hermès produced the first Birkin bag - now, thirty-five years later, the bag is still thriving. It has an extremely elitist reputation for being a status symbol, as well as a luxury handbag that offers everything you could possibly need. Carefully crafted in Gold Togo leather, this Birkin is elegant, elegant and sophisticated. Discreet and understated, the Birkin gives off a real "if you know, you know aesthetic". An absolute must-have for any woman in love with luxury, the Birkin is the ultimate addition to any luxury handbag collection.

title: Birkin 35 leather handbag
description:
Birkin 35 Togo Handbag 
 Color: B5 Ruby Purchased from Hermes 434 North Rodeo Drive Beverly Hills, CA, USA Year: 2011 [O] 
 The bag has been very well maintained for 9 years. I love it so much but rarely use it as I'm not tall enough to carry a 35 for my daily bag. I uploaded photos of the bottom four corners and you can see from there that this bag is in great condition. 
 I do the maintenance of this bag periodically with luxury care services. The leather is very shiny and smooth. Togo leather has a very coarse grain and that's exactly what I love about it. It makes a girl look beautiful and chic. The bag comes with its dustbag, raincoat and a small booklet. The receipt is in the photos, but I have covered all the personal information on it. Honestly, it's not easy to give up and I'm in no rush to sell this baby. But it's just such a waste to confine him to my apartment years after years. I hope he can find a good home in this community .... NO scratches except those on the bottom corners (see photos), no stains, no tints. Even the handles look very new as I always wrap them with Hermès ribbons.

title: Birkin 35 leather handbag
description:
The iconic Birkin 35 in a rare BISCUIT color, a neutral for ages, matches any occasion or outfit for that final polished touch 🖤 
 Palladium trims and grained togo leather complete the look. 
 square (2008), this bag comes with its dust bag, its protection against the rain and its booklet, a Hermès ribbon (which I find chic on the handles of a neutral bag) and a FREE silk Twilly to make the bag work with any color you choose 😍 
 
 The bag is in a nice little used condition. The corners are perfect. There are only a few slight marks on the hardware and (tiny) inside, all seen in the photo. The handles show signs of wear due to the color. Obviously easily masked (if desired) by a twilly or ribbon, as shown in the photos. 
 This is the only reason why I am announcing this beautiful bag at this great price, and in "good condition". Nothing else to report 
 
 The felt protection in the photos might not come with the bag because I seem to have misplaced it. My apologies if this will be the case 🙏

title: Birkin 25 leather handbag
description:
Hermes Rose Ete Baby Birkin 25 
 
 Genuine Hermes Birkin 25 Rose Eté Swift Leather 
 Palladium Hardware 
 Y Stamp, 2020 
 Mint in box . Keep fresh. Impeccable condition (with plastic on the material) 
 Perfect gift! Comes in a complete set with bell, lock, keys, raincoat, dustbag, Hermès box and receipt 
 This tender Rose Eté Baby Birkin is simply superb. 
 Rose Eté is a soft and exquisite rose that evokes the delicate femininity of a peony. 
 A precious piece of jewelry enhanced with fresh palladium hardware. 
 A truly exquisite and modern combination! 
 In luscious Swift leather that's more durable than you might think. 
 If you don't have a Birkin baby yet, you must! 
 So easy to get in and out, and holds longer than you think. 
 Beyond perfection from day to night! 
 Wear it with sneakers and jeans; wear it with heels and a cocktail dress. 
 Don't miss it - Rose Eté may be even prettier than Sakura in the 25cm Birkin size. 
 This rare and special piece of jewelry will turn heads wherever you go!
Packaging: Original box

title: Birkin 30 leather handbag
description:
Hermes LIMITED EDITION AND RARE 30cm Gold & Marron d'Inde Clemence Leather & Ficelle Nilo Lizard Club Birkin Bag with Permabrass Hardware


P Square, 2012
Excellent Condition
14" Width x 10" Height x 7" Depth
The limited edition Club Birkin line is incredibly rare, and gives a sporting life look to the iconic handbag. With the unique striping pattern that exudes luxury sport, this bag is a capstone piece to any Hermes collection. This bag is done in a fabulous display of Gold and Marron d'Inde Clemence Leather, partitioned by stripes of Ficelle Varanus Niloticus Lizard. This bag features two rolled handles, Permabrass Hardware, and a flap top with a turnlock closure. The interior is done in Marron d'Inde Chevre Leather, featuring one slip pocket and one zip pocket. This bag includes two keys, a lock, and a clochette.

This bag is in Excellent Condition. There is very light scratching to the hardware. This bag includes an Hermes dustbag, protective felt, box & official receipt.
Packaging: Original box

title: Birkin 30 crocodile handbag
description:
Little wonder of the House of Hermès, Birkin 30 CACAO colors, in niloticus crocodile, the distribution of the scales is just of rare perfection. Golden attributes, canvas inner lining giving it a very comfortable weight to wear. Inside a large storage compartment on one side and two smaller the other. Very little worn and still perfectly maintained. All the accessories are present: padlock with niloticus lining, two keys, bell and zipper, rain protection, two dust-bags, Hermès leather booklet and its recent maintenance sheet. The bag being more than ten years old (letter E in a square) and still having its original appearance as if it were much more recent. I made replace for the sake of perfection the attributes which therefore have their protective plastics. 
 Note, very small scratches under the 4 feet on the bottom of the bag and a very slight mark on the inside of the bag. You can see it in the photos. 
 The December 2019 invoice following the visit to Ateliers Hermès will be sent to the purchaser, it includes the serial number of the attributes enabling this little gem to be clearly identified. The CACAO color which is no longer available is surprising and changing depending on the lighting, it is for me a success in this choice of tones and this leather is of remarkable suppleness and softness :-)
Packaging: Dustbag, Original box

title: Birkin 35 leather handbag
description:
Hermès Birkin 35 Beige Parchemin Togo Sac à main en cuir plaqué or avec quincaillerie 
 [
 Hermès Birkin Bag 35 en cuir Togo avec garniture dorée, cette couleur s'appelle Parchemin. Une nuance chaude et neutre de blanc cassé / beige. 
 
 Fermeture à bascule avant, clochette avec serrure et deux clés, et poignées roulées doubles. Le cuir Togo a un grain visible, est souple et pourtant robuste et ferme. Tient très bien sa forme, est anti-rayures et a un effet «mat». 
 
 Traditionnellement, un caractère alphabétique est donné au sac pour marquer l'année de sa fabrication. Ce personnage se trouve au bout de la ceinture de fermeture. Entre 1945 et 1970, seul un caractère a été utilisé, plus tard ils y ont mis un cercle ou un carré. Des caractères supplémentaires indiquent la section de l'atelier où se trouve l'artisan. 
 
 Ce sac porte le cachet N dans un carré, ce qui nous indique qu'il date de 2010. 
 
 Caractéristiques surpiqûres ton sur ton et le cuir est fini dans une couleur marron à la coutures sur le dessus, en bas quatre clous dorés pour la protection. 
 
 L'intérieur est doublé de cuir lisse de la même couleur Parchemin. Une poche sans et une poche avec fermeture éclair qui contient une tirette gravée HERMÈS. 
 Ce sac est porté, mais en très bon état! Quelques rayures sur les plots en bas. Et le matériel sur les ceintures de fermeture présente également de légères rayures dues à l'utilisation. Livré avec dustbag, clochette, serrure et jeu de clés. 
 
 Couleur: Parchemin 
 
 Matière: Cuir Togo 
 
 Mesures: L: 35cm H: 26cm P: 19cm [[ 2]] 
 Fabriqué en France.

 This bag has been worn with great care and consistently praised as the most interesting "neutral"! 
 
 This pretty lady comes with her dustbag, mini dustbag, matching Fjord bell, keys and padlock, rain cover and booklet. Stamp date J in a square.

title: Birkin 25 leather handbag
description:
Very rare limited Hermes Birkin 25cm Sellier Etoupe Epsom in leather and PHW 
 
 The Birkin Sellier bag was introduced in 2014 as a limited edition model. With the growing popularity around the Kelly Sellier bag, it is not surprising that Hermès has decided to reissue a limited edition of the Birkin Seller bag in 2020 
 
 This piece never worn / used or worn is one example, and unlike the original version, today's Sellier Birkins have fully lined interiors with all the classic pockets we've come to expect. This bag is triple special because of its color and material. 
 
 With only a few in circulation, the Birkin Sellier bag was reserved for VIPS, loyal Hermès customers and celebrities. That being said, whenever a few hit the aftermarket or a pre-loved website, the price tag was astronomical due to the limited nature of this bag. 
 
 For all FOMO fashionistas, here is your chance 😉 
 The bag 👜 will come as in the Hermés store with the Hermés box, the lock and the PHW key, the rain protection, felt and protective covers. Enjoy your shopping 🛍

title: Birkin 35 leather bag
description:
The iconic Birkin bag, in the iconic ETOUPE color (medium gray with warm mink undertones). Literally matches everything in your wardrobe, one of the wonder colors from the H magic palette 🖤🖤🖤 
 
 This Birkins bag is available in size 35 in the rare (for this color, in particular) FJORD leather. A leather that is distinguished by its flat and large semi-matt grains. He sometimes has veins that annoy some collectors. This version in Fjord leather has no veins. 
 Fjord leather is weather resistant and can withstand a lot of use, unlike many other H leathers, while being a fine, fine leather itself. 
 Perfect for anyone who wants to use a Birkin in a perfectly dry and sunny climate 🤣 
 
 n amazing addition to anyone's collection and a perfect place to start property plans Birkin, at a very advantageous price 😍 
 
 Delivered with its dustbag, storage bag, mini dustbag for its bell, padlock and keys, rain protection, protective felt, Hermès booklet. 
 
 In excellent condition, only a little friction on the bottom as usual with Birkin bags, very few scratches on the hardware and some marks inside (a few tiny feathers), all clearly illustrated. 
 
 Images of the date stamp, not very clearly legible however. 
 
 
 Please take a look at my many other amazing pieces at friendly prices 🖤

title: Birkin 30 leather handbag
description:
100% Authentic Hermes Birkin 30 Black Veau C Risp Leather Gold Hardware Bag 
 
 By the house of Hermès, here we have this stylish Birkin 30 bag in black leather with gold hardware. 
 Hermes is known for its impeccable craftsmanship and high quality. 
 Hermes Birkin was inspired by Jane Birkin and is one of the most sought after handbags in the world. 
 A timeless classic that never goes out of style. 
 Handcrafted from the highest quality leather by skilled artisans, it takes long hours of rigorous effort to assemble a Birkin. 
 Made in France from fine leather in an elegant black color, the bag features double top rolled handles, flap and strap closure, gold plated hardware including twist lock and two keys. 
 The bag comes with gold plated hardware and has a spacious leather lined interior that houses a slip and a zippered pocket. 
 Birkin 30 can contain all your daily needs and more. 
 There has never been a Birkin that was not beautiful, invest in this collector's item as it retains its value year after year! 
 The superb bag is in excellent condition. 
 The bag was purchased on 03/2018 and will be delivered with the receipt. 
 Some of the devices before still have their protective tape still in place. 
 Used only twice with slight scratches on the front hardware and the base metal protective studs. 
 
 Color: Black 
 Material: Leather 
 Material: Gold plated 
 Approximate dimensions: W: 30cm x H: 22cm x D: 16cm [ [2]] Handle drop: 10cm 
 Made in France 
 Condition: Very good occasion 
 Delivered with: Booklet, Lock, Keys, Bell, Sleeper, Raincoat, Hermès box, receipt

title: Birkin 40 leather bag
description:
Hermes Birkin 40 cm handbag in brown taurillon clémence leather. 
 
 Who doesn't like dark brown? 
 
 Other than gold, the other all-time favorite color for women looking for their first Birkin, is Dk Brown. 
 Suitable for all occasions, versatile with all styles of clothing, this is the timeless fashion color. There is arguably no color more timeless and classic than dark brown and it will be loved by everyone forever. 
 
 The beauty of Clémence leather is that it develops character as it ages and after use. 
 
 This leather is the epitome of premium quality with its delicate finish and serves to accentuate a look reminiscent of femininity. 
 
 Savor the soft and supple texture of Hermès leather and find out how this durable grained leather is also a sturdy material as it resists scratches and dirt even when used daily.

title: Birkin 35 leather handbag
description:
En cuir Epsom Gold surpiqué blanc, ce Hermès Birkin 35 me fait penser à un cartable à l'ancienne, mais avec panache pendant des jours! Le rabat se ferme à l'aide de sangles et d'un fermoir à fermoir doré qui s'ouvre sur une doublure en cuir ton sur ton avec une poche zippée et une poche coulissante à l'intérieur. Portez ce Birkin dans la main avec sa goutte de 4 pouces ou sur le bras pour garder vos mains libres. En très bon état et estampillé d'un J dans un carré, il est livré avec une serrure, des clés, une clochette et un dustbag et a des traces d'usure sur les pieds, les coins et un peu sur la visserie. Cette Birkin a un peu de mou mais quatre pieds pour la garder debout et en forme de navire!
